====== H6471: פַּעַם ======

===== Source =====

or (feminine)   ; from  H6470 ;

===== Meaning =====

a  stroke , literally or figuratively (in various applications, as follow)

===== Definitions =====

  - stroke

===== Usage =====

anvil, corner, foot(-step), going, (hundred-) fold, × now, (this)   once, order, rank, step,   thrice, (often-), second, this, two) time(-s), twice, wheel.
